README - Spanish Learning App

Introduction
The Spanish Learning App is a Python application designed to help users improve their Spanish language skills through interactive quizzes. Utilizing the Kivy library, this application provides an engaging and user-friendly interface for learning Spanish vocabulary and sentence translations.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Features
Word Quiz: Test your knowledge of Spanish vocabulary by translating English words to Spanish.
Sentence Translation: Practice translating Spanish sentences into English with multiple-choice options.
Special Characters: Easily add Spanish characters to your answers via a convenient dropdown menu.
Progress Tracking: Keep track of how many questions you've answered correctly or incorrectly.
Navigation: Easily return to the main menu from any quiz.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Run
Install Python: Ensure you have Python installed on your system.
Clone Repository: Clone this repository to your local machine.
Navigate to Directory: Open a terminal and navigate to the project directory.
Install Dependencies: Run the following command to install the required dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Launch Application: Execute the script by running:
python main.py
Select a Quiz: Choose between the Word Quiz and Sentence Translation to start practicing.
Use Special Characters: Click the 'Spanish Characters' button to add Spanish characters to your answer.
Answer Questions: Type your answer in the input field and click 'Submit' to check your answer.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Technologies Used
Python: The core programming language used for development.
Kivy: An open-source Python library for developing multitouch applications.
random: Python library for generating random elements, used for randomizing quiz questions.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Acknowledgments
Special thanks to the developers and community behind Python and Kivy for providing the tools to create this learning application. Enjoy learning and improving your Spanish language skills!

